        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Remember to budget for ongoing costs (£100-500/month) and factor in the long-term value. A well-built website that ranks on Google, converts visitors, and requires minimal maintenance pays for itself many times over.</p>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">The cheapest option is rarely the best value. Invest in solid foundations — the right tech stack, proper SEO, and clean code — and your website becomes an asset that grows with your business rather than a liability that needs replacing in two years.</p>

